Humans are the most predominant race in the world of Darkwind. 
They are the not the strongest, quickest, smartest, or otherwise best 
race, but they are the most adaptable, and this is its own strength. 
That and sheer numbers ensure the continued survival of the human 
race. Human are generally liked, or at least tolerated, by other races, 
and in return generally tolerate all the others. This makes them 
more capable of ruling large dominions and becoming great heroes in 
many realms.

Humans' main advantage is their versatility. They can be in any guild,
and receive a small bonus to all experience earned.
 
Humans may join any guild.
